        <mxCell id="pipeline-legend" value="SharePoint → Foundry IQ Sync Pipeline&#xa;&#xa;① Timer triggers Azure Function (every N min)&#xa;② Function authenticates via Entra ID (SPN from Key Vault)&#xa;③ Pulls documents via Graph API (through Azure Firewall)&#xa;④ Writes documents to Blob Storage (via Private Endpoint)&#xa;⑤ AI Search Indexer crawls Blob (Shared Private Link)&#xa;⑥ Foundry Agent queries AI Search for knowledge" style="text;html=1;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=#FFF9CC;strokeColor=#D6B656;fontColor=#333333;rounded=1;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;spacingRight=10;strokeWidth=2;" parent="1" vertex="1">
